annotationA: Lethal (2) 37Cb; ATP binding; ATP-dependent RNA helicase activity; nucleic acid binding; RNA helicase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: mRNA splicing, via spliceosome; neurogenesis
annotationB: Probable U2 small nuclear ribonucleoprotein A; U2A is a protein component of the U2 snRNP. The U2 snRNP combines with other snRNPs on the pre-mRNA to assemble a spliceosome
